title: We Are Haunted By These Taylor Swift Lyrics
description:
Taylor Swift has some hauntingly beautiful lyrics, and these are some that we just can't seem to shake them off. Lacey, Amy, Ana and Nick pick some of their favs lyrics and explain why it continues to haunt them.
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? Lots of ways to contact us.
